                <li>• <strong>Unrealistic Expectations:</strong> AI is not a magic solution</li>
                <li>• <strong>Poor Data Quality:</strong> Garbage in, garbage out</li>
                <li>• <strong>Lack of Governance:</strong> No clear policies and procedures</li>
                <li>• <strong>Insufficient Testing:</strong> Rushing to production without proper validation</li>
                <li>• <strong>Ignoring Ethics:</strong> Not considering bias and fairness</li>
                <li>• <strong>No Change Management:</strong> Failing to prepare the organization</li>
              </ul>
